  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p>We welcome applicants who are SG Citizens/SPR (staying in SG).<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Delivery & Logistics Duties:-</strong></u></p><p>- Promptly deliver to assigned places.</p><p>- Pick & Pack.</p><p>- Assist in receiving incoming goods.</p><p>- Loading up goods for delivery.</p><p>- Delivery vehicle will be provided.</p><p>- Upon confirmation, the vehicle can be driven back to your residence.<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Remuneration:-</strong></u></p><p>- Salary Package will include AWS & variable bonus.</p><p>- Experience & forklift licence will be considered in the remuneration.</p><p>- Upon confirmation, salary will be revised.<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Environment:-</strong></u></p><p>- Friendly setting & colleagues.</p><p>- Convenient location in the West side (Bukit Batok/Bukit Timah).</p><p>- Working hours:- 9am - 6pm.</p><p>- 5-day work week.<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Time of interview</strong></u>:-</p><p>- Tuesday to Friday (1pm to 5.30pm)</p><p>- <strong>This is NOT a Walk-In Interview</strong>. Please send in your application. We will contact you for an interview appointment.<br /></p><p><br /><u><strong>Public Transport to our location</strong></u>:-</p><p>If coming from Hillview MRT, please take Bus - 176, 653, 963, 970 (3 bus stops)</p><p>If coming from Bukit Batok MRT, take Bus 177 from Interchange before 840am or Bus 176 opposite Blk 628 (6 bus stops).</p>",
