    "description": "<p>Rein Biotech Services Pte Ltd was founded in 1997. We started our business focusing on using biotechnology in helping farming activities in aquaculture, agriculture &amp; aquatic hobbies. This led to our foray into the distribution business when our products were being sought after by hobbyists. We further expanded our business to all types of pets since and is one of the most comprehensive pet products distributor in our region, representing a wide spectrum of high quality, award winning and highly sought after brands from all over the world.</p>",
